p.text: Login independent of social networking account.
The app is based on the concept of real-time ride-sharing.
It is an app that uses the most common relationship among humans: "strangers" and turns it into something else by joining their paths literally!
Much more than just a ride sharing app.
Efficient utilization of this space to reduce carbon footprint is the need of the hour.
Non-compliance and non-availability of autorickshaws and taxis
Increasing rise in usage of public transport leads to crowded buses
Application to be made on Android platform
To create a modern and mobile approach
To prove to be of significant social and environmental benefit.
Parse is a host service, providing backend services to end-user applications.
Objective in creating this application is to help the user find a ride easily as well as cheaply
This application will help users combat the continuous high rise in traveling expenses by sharing the cost of travel with other users.

Real-time ride-sharing applications like ours will in turn help in assuaging traffic, help save fuel, money and time and thus revolutionize the way we have been traveling in a population intense city like ours.
Not enough security for female travelers
